1.title: Cambrie vs. Jamie: Game On!
1.plot: It's a whole new world - pageants are the new sports! Stakes are higher, competition is fierce & you can't win without the right coach. Pageant season begins with blood, snot and vomit as Cambrie's Court clashes with rival team, the Sassy Supremes.

2.title: Cambrie vs. Jamie: Welcome to the Glitz Jungle!
2.plot: The Jungle Safari Pageant roars on. Cambrie's kids are on point; Jaimie's aren't. Kallyn gets confused. Selyse wanders off stage. Fed up, Kim asks Cambrie to coach Selyse. Which team will reign Mega Ultimate Grand Supreme and drive off in a new car?

3.title: Cambrie vs. Jamie: The Birth Certificate
3.plot: Jaimie and Cambrie take their teams back to the west coast to prepare for Gemstars Heroes v Villains Pageant-run by Jaimie's mom! Tensions on both sides flare as one mom gets kicked off the team while another is accused of lying about her kid's age.

4.title: Cambrie vs. Jamie: The Birth Certificate, Part 2
4.plot: Tensions rise all week between Cambrie's Court and the Sassy Supremes. Come pageant day, both teams are fired up and ready for the battle. But a disastrous series of events at Gemstars Heroes v Villains leads to an outcome that shocks everyone.

5.title: The One to Beat
5.plot: Cambrie's on her home turf and up against Top Model's Amanda & Nisa. Each team thinks makeup man Mykel is THEIR secret weapon - until he double books himself out to both teams. Can Top Model top girl Landree pull off a win despite the debacle?

6.title: Just Hit Somebody!
6.plot: Top Model finds a last minute replacement for overbooked Mykel, so Landree & Addison are able to compete! Cambrie's team struggles on stage and off. One mom punches another over a rumor. At the end of the day, all three coaches end up in tears.

7.title: The Georgia Jinx
7.plot: After a tough loss to the Top Model, Cambrie's Court travels to Georgia for the Cowgirls and Crowns Pageant. Cambrie brings heavy hitter (and Trump supporter!) Landri, to battle Top Model's big winner Saymone. Can Cambrie's Court make a comeback?

8.title: Here Come the Animals!
8.plot: It's time for the annual Me and My Pet Pageant! It's Cambrie vs. past Pet winners Alycesaundra and Giavanna and their coach/mom Kelly. Luckily Cambrie has Kailia, and cousins Callyn and Emily in her corner. When competition begins, it becomes a zoo!

9.title: The Goat Poop Incident
9.plot: At the Me and My Pet Pageant, chaos ensues when Aly and Gia's goat, Blackberry, allegedly poops all over the floor - and neither Kelly nor her husband will clean it up! Will the goat poop incident distract the contestants from performing their best?

10.title: The Return of Eden Wood
10.plot: Eden Wood is back where her career began: Universal Royalty in Austin, TX! This season, Eden will be judging the tough competition between Cambrie's Court heavy hitter, Abby, Jaimie's sassy girl, Kaydence, and returning UR champ, Princess Mehayle.

11.title: Emergency at Universal Royalty
11.plot: For Princess Mehayle, mom Sharilynne and coach Nikki Nicole, pageant day at Universal Royalty only goes from bad to worse! After fierce competition and a slew of mistakes and mishaps on stage, crowning isn't the only shocking event of the day.

12.title: The Final Showdown
12.plot: Pageant season's big finale, International Fresh Faces in Gatlinburg, brings back all this season's favorites. After a very heated rivalry, the Sassy Supremes and Cambrie's Court face off for the last time. Who will be the supreme pageant team?

13.title: A Team's Revenge
13.plot: In the conclusion of Int. Fresh Faces in TN, the tension between the Sassy Supremes and Cambrie's Court mounts. After two long days of competition, Sassy mom, Jessica snaps and confronts Kim, and crowning reveals the mega ultimate supreme team.

1.title: Universal Royalty National Pageant
1.plot: Everything is big in Texas, especially the stakes at Universal Royalty! In this pageant, mothers and daughters compete against each other to win the title and $5,000 cash!! The stakes are high, and so is the pressure for one dedicated pageant dad.

2.title: Miss Georgia Spirit
2.plot: This first annual pageant brings in girls of all ages from all over Georgia, and range from full glitz to au naturale. All natural Kayleigh, 6 competes with pageant pro Story, 5 for the title, and it's not over until the recount!

3.title: Universal Royalty State Pageant
3.plot: Austin, Texas is home of Universal Royalty's state pageant. Texas is a staple in the pageant world and the competition is sure to be fierce. The judging happens on stage while the drama ensues off stage as each mom tries to prove their baby is beautiful.

4.title: Chitlin Strut
4.plot: This pageant in South Carolina may be held in a very small town, but it draws girls from many states who have big dreams of stardom. Last year's winner, Madison, has stiff competition in glitz girl Aubrey, and both have a Mom eyeing the prize.

5.title: Kentucky Southern Celebrity
5.plot: This pageant in the small town of Inez, Kentucky draws kids from numerous states for the opportunity to 'make dreams come true one crown at a time.' 7 year old Holly faces off against the confident Jadyn to win the title of Ultimate Grand Supreme.

6.title: Southern Celebrity Wonderland Pageant
6.plot: With 90 contestants at the Wonderland pageant in Charleston, WV, there is plenty of great competition! But all eyes are on Payton, who at six years old, is hoping for a Grand Supreme title to mark his retirement from pageantry.

7.title: Stars of Pennsylvania
7.plot: The stage is full of glitz and glamour at this pageant in Pittsburg, PA. Even a massive snowstorm can't keep the diehard pageant kids away. For the Ayala sisters, Angela, 8, Addison, 5, and Aliana, 2, it is their first time doing a glitz pageant!

8.title: Texas Walk of Fame
8.plot: At the Texas Walk of Fame pageant boys and girls come from all over to win the title and $1000 cash! Feisty brothers Maverick, 2, and Hayden, 3 are completely unpredictable on stage and newcomer Taralyn, 4, battles rival Faith, 5, for the ultimate prize!

9.title: Darling Divas
9.plot: Brooklyn, NY is the home of the Darling Divas pageant where your inner diva shines! Little princess, Paige, 4, does some unusual preparation with a chiropractic adjustment but it's pageant pro, Essence, 6, who steals the show with her Tina Turner routine.

1.title: Universal Royalty Pageant
1.plot: Don't mess with Texas, especially when the stakes are high at the Universal Royalty Pageant. The competition is fierce between a full glitz pro, Eden, 4 and fan favorite, Cameron, a seven year old pageant veteran.

2.title: Queen and Kings of America
2.plot: 4 year-old Katlyn's family prays for pageant success. Ava, 3 and her mom channel spirits. For Iyslah,7, it is her first glitz pageant. At the Queen of the Galaxy pageant, see if any spiritual guidance or beginners luck helps win the Ultimate Grand Supreme

3.title: West Virginia Walk of Fame
3.plot: This West Virginia pageant may be held in a small town, but the Walk of Fame pageant is big time. Hannah, 7, is coming off a two-year hiatus in the pageant world. Her competition, Jayla, 6, brings along a secret weapon, her father, a true pageant Dad!

4.title: American Regal Gems
4.plot: East Coast Pageants draw a variety of glitz girls from New York to Utah. Victoria, 6, embarks on her first full glitz pageant against heavy hitter Morgan, 7 and Elexis, 6 who is hoping her winning edge will be her double entry in the talent category.

5.title: National Gold Coast
5.plot: This National Gold Coast pageant is the real Little Miss Sunshine that brings together the best of the west. Newcomer Rylan, 4, is prepared and ready to give 110%. Competing against her is Emily, 4, a local favorite and Alicia, 7, a pageant pro.

6.title: Beautiful Dolls
6.plot: North Carolina holds high-end pageants where the glitz and glitter get you the gold. Kailee, is a pageant veteran at age 5, competing against shy Skyler, 4, and the Gary Sisters Sterling 5, and Paris, 3.

7.title: Dazzling Dreams
7.plot: Marmaduke, Arkansas draws a big crowd for their Babes of Summer pageant. Hope, 6, is the local heavy hitter taking on Sara, 4, and the Sprinkle Sisters who are a triple threat to beat at ages 6, 8 and 10.

8.title: Outlaw Pageant
8.plot: In West Virginia, the Outlaw pageant draws the most serious of competition. Isabella, 6, comes all the way from Michigan to compete against WV's true beauty Jayden, 5. Alongside these two is the local top contender Haley, 6, who is in it to win it.

9.title: Gold Coast OC Spring Pageant
9.plot: The Golden Coast of California is host to this high stakes pageant as newcomer Sparkal, 7, takes on returning heavy hitter Michaela, 8, and seasoned pro Cassidy, 7, where Beauty, Talent, and Swimwear will decide who will be the Ultimate High Point Winner.

10.title: Little Miss
10.plot: Mississippi plays host to the Tiny Miss USA pageant as Kragen, 8, vies for the title 'that got away', against rising star Mckenzie, 7, and pageant veteran Bayleigh, 5. Competition heats up, as these pageant hopefuls bring their best to take home the crown

11.title: America Fabulous Faces: Hawaii
11.plot: America's Fabulous Faces takes us to the islands of Hawaii as Aaliyah, 5, competes against fellow islander Jessie, 9, and mainlander Lindsay, 7. Competition heats up as these three beauties have their eyes on the crown and the $1000 cash prize.

12.title: Universal Miss and Master International
12.plot: UMMI brings the best pageant beauties from all over the country as Jordyn, 6, looks to bring home another UMMI crown. Standing in her way Miranda, 7 and Halia, 9

13.title: Arizona Gold Coast
13.plot: Competition heats up in Arizona, as glitz girl Charlie, 4, has high hopes in winning big in this years Gold Coast Pageant.

14.title: Little Miss Glitz
14.plot: Florida brings out great competition for their Little Miss Glitz Pageant as top contenders Cruz Rodriguez, 1, goes up against Maddox Herrera, 1, and cutie Kinley Rice, 3. From top performances to constant tantrums, it's anyone's guess who will win.

15.title: Southern Majestic Pageants
15.plot: Charlotte, North Carolina brings the heavy hitters in the pageant world as Victoria, 7, Chelsea, 10, and Arianna, 5, all vie to be grand supreme in the Southern Majestic Pageant.

16.title: Southern Glitz Open State
16.plot: It's the Southern Glitz Open State pageant as Sadie, 4, brings all her spunk to compete against Isabella, 3, who's mother will make sure she's on her A-game. They'll all be chasing Bella, 5, who already holds 8 Ultimate Grand Supreme titles.

17.title: Gold Coast California Grand State Finals
17.plot: The Gold Coast Pageant is home to some of the best pageant beauties of the southwest. Larua, 6, will try to shine with her pizza tossing routine but will it be enough to beat Diamond, 4, and Nicole, 5, who will do everything to impress the judges?

18.title: Universal Royalty National Pageant 2
18.plot: With $5000 at stake, pageant superstar Eden, 4, will work the stage like never before to win back her crown, but Janene, 5, will pull out all the stops to beat her rival. Meanwhile, veteran Brooke, 9, looks to add another title to her already long list

1.title: Le Maison de Paris
1.plot: It's the Le Maison de Paris Pageant as pageant veteran Alex, 9, has her eye on the top title. Also competing is Daisy, 7, whose dance moves are sure to draw attention and show-stopper Makenzie, 4, who brings more than just a winning attitude.

2.title: Director's Choice
2.plot: It's the Director's Choice Pageant in Paragould, Arkansas as Carissa, 2, is a rising pageant star with loads of personality. Standing in her way Lexie, 5, a heavy hitter in the pageant world, and Zander, 5, a pageant diva in the boy's division.

3.title: America's Treasured Dollz
3.plot: Large prizes and lots of cash draw many contestants to the America's Trezured Dollz pageant in Nashville, Tennessee. But the pageant is off to a bad start when the pageant director is missing leading to an outraged crowd.

4.title: America's Best Pageant
4.plot: America's Best Pageant may also have America's most dedicated pageant contestants. Taleah, 4, Jasmine, 5, and Lauren, 7, are all from families who have sacraficed a lot to get here, but which beauty will rise to the top to take home the big crown.

5.title: Darling Divas
5.plot: It's tears, tantrums and tie-breakers that keep the Southern Celebrity pageant buzzing. Aniston, 3, Teeghan, 3, and April, 6, are all here to compete, but only one can be crowned the Ultimate Grand Supreme.

6.title: Southern Celebrity: NC Winter Wonderland
6.plot: It's tears, tantrums and tie-breakers that keep the Southern Celebrity pageant buzzing. Aniston, 3, Teeghan, 3, and April, 6, are all here to compete, but only one can be crowned the Ultimate Grand Supreme.

7.title: Winter Beauties
7.plot: Another Ultimate Grand Supreme title is up for grabs as Texas hosts the Winter Beauties Pageant. Kayleigh, 3, will compete alone on stage for the first time against heavy hitters Brooklyn, 10, and Brittannie, 9. Will she be ready to shine solo?

8.title: Fantasy Pageant
8.plot: It's Show Me Smiles Fantasy Pageant in Bernie, Missouri. Haley, 8, is an out of this world competitor with an unforgettable father/daughter performance, but will Lexie, 9, stand in her way. Meanwhile, Olivia, 4, may shock them all.

9.title: Royal Essence
9.plot: The storm clouds are brewing at the Royal Essence pageant, but it is all sunshine and smiles on stage. See Kaylee, 10, Darrick, 4, and Olivia, 3, all battle for the top crown and cash in this episode of Toddlers and Tiaras.

10.title: Gold Coast, Arizona
10.plot: Makenzie, 4, is back and at the top of her game. Twins, Scarlett and Isabella, 1, are a dynamic duo supported heavily by their mother's millions. Danielle, 8, is very confident in her good looks and wants all eyes on her during this competition.

11.title: Universal Royalty, Texas
11.plot: All the glitz and glamour shine on stage at the Universal Royalty pageant in Austin, Texas. Daddy's girl Ava, 3, attempts once again to live up to her father's big dreams of success but Mia, 2, proves to be a showstopper.

12.title: Fancy Faces
12.plot: Falls, follies and pulled follicles are all part of the fun as Oklahoma City plays host to the Fancy Faces pageant. Watch pageant beauties SamiJo, Jackynn, and Alexis all vie for the top crown and find out who has this year's fanciest face!

13.title: Viva Las Vegas
13.plot: Gold Coast brings contestants from all over the country for an intense competition at the entertainment capital of the world for their Viva Las Vegas Pageant. Competition heats up as only one beauty will be worthy of the High Point title.

14.title: Mardi Gras
14.plot: Plenty of girls, beads and glitz all promise a good show at the Mardi Gras pageant in Darien, Georgia. The stage is set for a serious competition. It will be a tough decision for these judges as they decide who is worthy of the top title.

15.title: Groovy Girls
15.plot: Texas is heating up, as Taralyn, 6, Brooklyn 5, and newcomer Zana, 6, all fight for the title of Ultimate Grand Supreme at the Groovy Girls pageant in Nacogdoches, Texas.

16.title: Southern Celebrity Ohio
16.plot: Trophies, crowns, and sashes are all at stake at this year's Southern Celebrity pageant in Athens, Ohio. The competition is fierce as Isabella, 7, Mercedes, 3, and Tiffany, 8, all vie for the top title and the prize money that goes with it.

17.title: International Fresh Faces
17.plot: Lily, 3, is a rough and tumble tot that her mom wants to soften up into a sweetie. Ashley-Noelle, 2, is following in her mom's pageantry footsteps and wants nothing but to win the crown. But will it be enough to beat determined performer Victoria, 7?

18.title: Rodeo Princess Pageant
18.plot: Pageant girls are rounding up for a showdown in Bridgeport, West Virginia at the Rodeo Princess Pageant. Who will lasso the biggest crown and take the top title? Only the judges can decide.

1.title: Universal Royalty: The Ultimate Showdown
1.plot: It's on for the fan-favorite Universal Royalty Pageant. This 80's themed Texas pageant is going to be the Ultimate Showdown between the two most famous girls to hit the pageant stage: MaKenzie and Eden.

2.title: Halloween Bash
2.plot: The competition is scary for Pentecostal mom Ca'Trina and daughter Saryniti at the Halloween Bash in Oklahoma City.

3.title: Circle City Stars and Cars
3.plot: Underdog Alaska, 7, turns it on in the final heat, but is it enough to win the race to Ultimate Grand Supreme?

4.title: Southern Celebrity Mini Nationals
4.plot: Pageant prince Brock, 7 steals the show at the Southern Celebrity Mini National Pageant with his jazz and gymnastics.

5.title: Universal Royalty Grand Nationals
5.plot: A stunning $10,000 prize is up for grabs at Universal Royalty Grand Nationals and everyone from toddler to teen wants it!

6.title: Rock Star Divas and Dolls
6.plot: The competition burns up the stage at Rock Star Diva and Dolls, but it's the offstage antics of Olivia that wow the crowd!

7.title: Miss Sugarplum Fairy
7.plot: Sisters Karley and Kylie compete against each other for the first time ever in the Miss Sugarplum Fairy pageant.

8.title: Glamorous Beauties
8.plot: Beauty is in the eye of the judges at Glamorous Beauties for three gorgeous contestants: Ally, Emerald and Baylen.

9.title: Rumble in the Jungle
9.plot: Pageant superstar and recording artist Eden defends her title at the Rumble in the Jungle in Louisville, Kentucky.

10.title: Gold Coast Las Vegas
10.plot: Las Vegas native showgirl in training Desiree, is serious about claiming her hometown title, Kayla may only be three, but has the stage presence of a pageant pro. Kailia, has performing in her blood, as her Vegas performer parents groom her to be a star.

11.title: Hearts and Crowns
11.plot: Maddy follows in her mom's glitz pageant footsteps, and even competes in her mom's padded Dolly Parton outfit! 10-year-old Queen teaches her mom the do's and don'ts of high glitz. Madison, keeps her mom on her toes with her unpredictable behavior.

12.title: Precious Moments Pageant
12.plot: Underdog Alana, 6, goes up against gum-smacking Heaven, 6, and chocolate lover Laci, 8, pulls out all the stops to get the judges' attention.

13.title: International Fresh Faces Missouri
13.plot: The rivalry is ON in Missouri as pageant pros Sydney and Maddison go head to head for the Ultimate Grand Supreme! Still learning the details is Paige, but has the charm of her sweet personality and quirky smile.

14.title: Storybook Pageant
14.plot: At the Storybook Pageant Berkeley, 4 has her routines down, but the morning of the pageant wakes up sick. Alessondra 9, rocks her 80's hair-do and long dress. Carley, 5, and her bestfriend/mom strive for perfection.

15.title: Southern Celebrity Glitzmas
15.plot: Siblings Riley, 5 and Bob, 6, steal the show at Southern Celebrity Glitzmas pageant with their "fierce" drag queen moves!

16.title: Island of Dreams Pageant
16.plot: Cadence, 8, has a secret weapon: her sass-talking Pageant Grandma. Two year-old Samara's mom is a tattooed, heavy metal singer. Pageant mom Kelly throws a full glitz fit when she thinks her daughter Natalie, 2 ,has lost the pageant.

17.title: America's Ultimate Beauty
17.plot: SamiJo, 2, Alexes, 3, and Annabella, 7 pull out all the stops in their American Wear to be America's Ultimate Beauty.

18.title: Crown Beauties
18.plot: It may be cold outside, but things are heating up in Hot Springs, Arkansas! Three girls and their coach moms from Perfection Studios face off: Adorable Penny Lane, 3, perfectionist Cassadee, 9, and wild child Torrann, 7.

1.title: Precious Moments Pageant 2011
1.plot: Underdog Alana, 6, goes up against gum-smacking Heaven, 6, and chocolate lover Laci, 8, pulls out all the stops to get the judges' attention.

2.title: Lollipops and Gumdrops Pageant
2.plot: Pageant star MaKenzie faces squabbling sisters Kaylie and Brooke, as well as Hailey, who is trained by a professional drag queen.

3.title: Universal Royalty Hollywood
3.plot: With $10,000 at stake at the Old Hollywood-themed pageant, tempers run high, and conspiracy theories abound with pageant moms. Mia, 5, Isys, 6, and Saliz, 7 are determined to win Ultimate Grand Supreme..

4.title: Glitzy Divas
4.plot: Paetynn, 4, Elesha, 5, and pro performer Daisy, 8, are out to swash buckle the competition at the Pirate Pageant in Nacogdoches, Texas.

5.title: Darling Divas New York
5.plot: At Darling Divas, Shian and Isabella go up against notorious Paisley to win the big title in the Big Apple.

6.title: Southern Celebrity: Fairytale Winter Pageant
6.plot: Pageant pro and fan favorite, Alaska, returns to the pageant stage with her outrageous mother, Lori, to claim yet another Ultimate Grand Supreme title. Newcomer, Gabbi and her mother, are outraged by Alaska's brazen self-confidence and are ready to rumble.

7.title: Beautiful Me Disco Pageant
7.plot: Three-year old Destiny's mom has pushed her credit cards to the limit to pay for her daughter's hobby. Three year-old Camari needs to bring her best to outshine two-year old Sami-Jo. But the real competition isn't between these two, it's their moms.

8.title: Circle City Wild West Showdown
8.plot: Sweet Daisy Mae, 8, sassy Bridget, 5, and firecracker Jacy, 8, compete in a wild west showdown to win a puppy.

9.title: Storybook Pageant: Diamonds
9.plot: Diamonds are a girls' best friend at the StoryBook Pageant in Harrisburg, Pennsylvania but chaos ensues for Kylie, 5, Trinity, 5, and Sienna, 4 when their score sheets are revealed.

10.title: Me and My Pet Pageant
10.plot: Karley, 6, Kali, 5, and twins Alycesaundra and Giavanna, 4 bring their pets to compete at the Me and My Pet Pageant.

11.title: America's Genuine Jewel Pageant
11.plot: Mackenzie, 4, Damitri'ana,8 and little person Lacy Mae,8 go to the ends of the earth to win at America's Genuine Jewel pageant with an around the world theme.

12.title: International Fresh Faces: Fairy Pageant
12.plot: Ava-Cate, 3, practices her booty smack while mom prays she doesn't do it on stage. Samantha, 7, is a perfectionist who has big expectations. Her biggest competition is the spunky Traven, 6, who wows the audience with his performances.

13.title: Mississippi Sweet Pea Pageant
13.plot: Contestants Emma 3, McKenzie, 5 and Liz, 7 are fired up to win the Mississippi Sweet Pea luau themed pageant. Who will wow the judges and who will fight back against their comments.

14.title: California Tropic Arizona
14.plot: Perfectionist Danielle, 10 and rivals Kayla, 4 and Kailia, 5 put it all on the line at the California Tropic Arizona pageant.

15.title: Miss Mardi Gras Madness
15.plot: Can Tori, 5, Amiya, 6 and Jasmine, 10 overcome their pageant day debacles and reign supreme at the Miss Mardi Gras Madness Pageant in Shreveport, Louisiana?

16.title: Out of This World Pageant
16.plot: Feisty Bella, 2, cutie Ava Lane, 3, and reserved Jayla, 7 hope their stars align at the Out of this World Pageant in Darien, Georgia.

17.title: Hollywood Stars Pageant
17.plot: Celebrity crazed Mia, 4, cutie Kelsey, 5 and super confident Casey, 7 compete for a Hollywood talent contract at the Hollywood Stars Pageant in Parsippany, New Jersey.

18.title: Georgia's Most Beautiful Girls: Going for Gold
18.plot: Honey Boo Boo, Alana, 6 is back and crazier than ever when she competes against Destiny, 5 and Deseray, 8. Every contestant is going for the gold at the Georgia's Most Beautiful Girls pageant in Atlanta, Georgia.

19.title: Universal Royalty Motown
19.plot: Mackenzie, 10, and her brother, Christian, 7 compete against feisty Jayla, 6 and newbie Chloe, 3 for $1,000 in the Universal Royalty Motown Pageant in Plano, Texas.

20.title: Little Mr. And Miss Nevada
20.plot: Twins Scarlett and Isabella, 3 compete against Georgina's students Elizabeth, 5 and Kylee, 6 at the Little Mr. and Miss Nevada Pageant in Las Vegas.

21.title: Beautiful Me: 50's Pageant
21.plot: Ava, 22 months, Emma, 8 and Destiny, 4 rock around the clock 50's style at the Beautiful Me Pageant in Gatlinburg, Tennessee.

22.title: Most Memorable Moments
22.plot:

23.title: Universal Royalty Christmas
23.plot: Ava, 3, Katlyn, 3 and pageant newbie Hailey, 9 compete for the greatest gift of Ultimate Grand Supreme at the Universal Royalty Christmas pageant in Austin, Texas.

24.title: Carolina Queens Pageant
24.plot: Glitz newbies Selena, 3, and Mackenzie, 6, face fierce Faithlyn, 9, at the Carolina Queens Pageant in Columbia, South Carolina.

25.title: Southern Elite: Cirque
25.plot: Jersie, 6, Ashley, 6 and rivals Gracie, 7 and Faithlyn, 9 all compete for the crown at the Southern Elite: Cirque Pageant in Lexington, Kentucky.

26.title: International Fresh Faces: Kentucky Derby
26.plot: The derby goes full glitz at the IFF Pageant in Lexington, Kentucky with contestants Kendyl, 18 months, Jozy, 3 and Alanna, 6.

27.title: California Tropic: Under the Sea Pageant
27.plot: Cariah, 4, Alyssa, 5, and Jordan, 9, go Under the Sea to compete at the California Tropic Pageant in Reno, Nevada.

28.title: A Glitzy Life for Me: Pirate Pageant
28.plot: Paetynn, 4, Elesha, 5, and pro performer Daisy, 8, are out to swash buckle the competition at the Pirate Pageant in Nacogdoches, Texas.

29.title: Stars 'n' Glitz: Fiesta
29.plot: It's a fiesta for Ariana, 7, Alyssa, 3 and Natali, 3 at the Stars Â'n Glitz Pageant in Charlotte, North Carolina.

30.title: Cheetah-licious Pageant
30.plot: Things get wild for Brooklyn, 21 months, Bella, 2, and Emma Belle, 5, at the Cheetahlicious Pageant in Quapaw, Oklahoma.

31.title: International Fresh Faces: Circus Pageant
31.plot: It's all beauty Under the Big Top as Oliviana, 22 months, Alivia, 4, and glitz newbie Katlyn, 6, vie for the circus crown at the IFF Pageant in Macon, Georgia.

1.title: Disco Fever Pageant
1.plot: Coffee loving Alexa, 2 goes up against diva Janeyah, 3 and her two moms as well as Brooke, 4 and her bodybuilder father JD. At the Disco Fever pageant, see whether Alexa melts-down after her sugar high wears off and Janeyah's prop passes the glitz test.

2.title: California Tropic: Sugar & Spice
2.plot: Distracted Bailey, 3 goes up against Daddy's girl Riley, 4 and Kelsie, 1 who gets a mayonnaise treatment on her hair. This pageant is explosive as one mother is banned!

3.title: Universal Royalty: Galaxy Queen
3.plot: 4 year-old Katlyn's family prays for pageant success. Ava, 3 and her mom channel spirits. For Iyslah,7, it is her first glitz pageant. At the Queen of the Galaxy pageant, see if any spiritual guidance or beginners luck helps win the Ultimate Grand Supreme

4.title: Las Vegas: LalapaZOOza
4.plot: It's all about the entrance when Elizabeth, 6 and her Noni return to compete against Ava, 5 and Mimi, 3. In Las Vegas it's anyone's chance to win over the drag queen celebrity-impersonated judges as they compete for the tallest trophy in pageant history!

5.title: When I Grow Up Pageant
5.plot: 23 month-old Lyric has a family of female wrestlers. Five year-old twins Giavanna and Alycesaundra are considered pageant royalty. At the When I Grow Up pageant, things heat up when an argument with the pageant director leads to police intervention.

6.title: Glitter Girls: Bollywood
6.plot: Two year-old Khloe's mom is proud to say she named her daughter after Khloe Kardashian. Ma'Leeh, 6, is new to the glitz pageant world and four year-old Brooklyn's mom, calls her a glitzy hillbilly. At the Bollywood pageant, see who takes the crown!

7.title: Starz-N-Glitz: Stone Age
7.plot: Charli 2, is a DIT (Diva in Training), Savannah, 3 hates pageants and loves hockey, Maddisyn-Rae, 2 loves eating her boogers. At the Queen of the Stone Age pageant in Charlotte, NC, will all 3 girls meltdown or make it to stage, or will their dads save

8.title: Around the World
8.plot: Brenna, 6, is back and is now a local celebrity that expects the royal treatment. Sophia-Rayne, 3, shows off some of her Native American roots with a glitz twist while Madison's coach seems to attract pageant drama at the Around the World Pageant in SC.

9.title: Me & My Pet: Tennessee
9.plot: Down in Tennessee, Lily 3, competes with her horse, Blackjack, but will her pony behave on stage? Gabby, 4 wrangles her guinea pig, Puddin with the help of her coach Katie. Rainbow Dash, 4 trains her dog, Titi, to perform in her Afro Circus routine.

10.title: Puttin' on the Glitz Pageant
10.plot: In White Plains, NY, Kelsie, 1 and her mom, Trystian, are back to redeem their name after getting banned from the pageant in Las Vegas. Brooklyn, 3 has a big personality she's not afraid to share.

11.title: If I Were a Rich Girl Pageant
